<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_29e8292e57f2.aspx"><b>鸿雁</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson29e8292e57f2">
<p>鸿雁于飞，肃肃其羽。之子于征，劬劳于野。爰及矜人，哀此鳏寡。<br />鸿雁于飞，集于中泽。之子于垣，百堵皆作。虽则劬劳，其究安宅？<br />鸿雁于飞，哀鸣嗷嗷。维此哲人，谓我劬劳。维彼愚人，谓我宣骄。</p>
</div>
